sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Orch as Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional)
    participant Health as Health Server<br/>8034/TCP HTTP<br/>Plaintext
    participant TGIS as TGIS Generation<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS (optional)
    participant NLP as Caikit NLP<br/>8085/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS (optional)
    participant Chunker as Caikit Chunkers<br/>8085/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS (optional)
    participant Detector as Detector Services<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Bearer (optional)
    participant OpenAI as OpenAI Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Bearer (optional)

    Note over Client,Detector: Flow 1: Classification with Text Generation (v1 Unary)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v1/task/classification-with-text-generation<br/>Headers: passthrough (X-Forwarded-Access-Token)
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict (gRPC)<br/>Chunk input text
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text segments
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Input detection on chunks<br/>Auth: Bearer (optional)
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection scores per chunk
    Note over Orch: Evaluate input detections<br/>against thresholds
    alt Input blocked
        Orch-->>Client: 200 OK with detection results (blocked)
    else Input passed
        Orch->>TGIS: Generate (gRPC)<br/>Text generation request
        TGIS-->>Orch: Generated text
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/generation<br/>Output detection on generated text
        Detector-->>Orch: Output detection scores
        Note over Orch: Evaluate output detections<br/>against thresholds
        Orch-->>Client: 200 OK with generation + detection results
    end

    Note over Client,OpenAI: Flow 2: OpenAI Chat Completions with Detection (v2 Streaming)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Headers: passthrough
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/chat<br/>Input detection on chat messages
    Detector-->>Orch: Input detection scores
    Note over Orch: Evaluate input detections
    alt Input passed
        Orch->>OpenAI: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>stream=true<br/>Auth: Bearer (optional)
        loop SSE Stream
            OpenAI-->>Orch: SSE chunk
            Orch-->>Client: SSE forwarded chunk
        end
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/generation<br/>Output detection on accumulated text
        Detector-->>Orch: Output detection scores
        Orch-->>Client: SSE final chunk with detections
    end

    Note over Client,Chunker: Flow 3: Streaming Content Detection (NDJSON)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/stream-content<br/>NDJSON stream
    Orch->>Chunker: BidiStreamingChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict (gRPC)<br/>Bidirectional streaming
    loop NDJSON Stream
        Client->>Orch: NDJSON line (text segment)
        Orch->>Chunker: Stream text chunk
        Chunker-->>Orch: Tokenized chunk
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Detection on chunk
        Detector-->>Orch: Detection scores
        Orch-->>Client: NDJSON response line with detections
    end

    Note over Client,Health: Health Check Flow
    Client->>Health: GET /health (8034/TCP, plaintext)
    Health-->>Client: 200 OK (package info)
    Client->>Health: GET /info (8034/TCP, plaintext)
    Health->>TGIS: grpc.health.v1.Health.Check
    Health->>NLP: grpc.health.v1.Health.Check
    Health->>Chunker: grpc.health.v1.Health.Check
    Health->>Detector: GET /health (8081/TCP)
    TGIS-->>Health: Health status
    NLP-->>Health: Health status
    Chunker-->>Health: Health status
    Detector-->>Health: Health status
    Health-->>Client: 200 OK (all service health statuses)
